{"tid":1481620,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]彩虹牛池灣被狗搞!","createTime":"2019-08-17T18:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:14:10.000Z","uid":135408,"like":280,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"3bcff0c047498bd8a9e030058a2d0934ae1ab76c","tid":1481620,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:47:24.000Z","msg":"0159 有三架警車黎左牛池灣 由中間六色紙組成的818已經完成<br />\n0215 遭疑似香港警察到場後撕毀只留下圖二，圖三等等 經一番努力後 於0228完成新818<br />\n0228 現場義工離開 拍攝現場圖片<br />\n<br />\n立此存證 敬請各方人士傳揚開去 <br />\n香港警察撕毀連儂牆上文宣及818字眼<br />\n<br />\n黑警 撕完唔撚洗負責任?<br />\n日撚日痴你上牆呀仆街 唔好以為冇人知啦<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ikk2mp0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fikk2mp0.jpg&h=e6be84ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CPOgYp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CPOgYp.jpg&h=5b7122ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MPYbZbN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMPYbZbN.jpg&h=e3a9241b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3HgqRP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3HgqRP.jpg&h=94f05e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OX3n5RR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOX3n5RR.jpg&h=b5729e3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c1ee97ce222fbb7c38266ae58de65563529b8d6","tid":1481620,"uid":135408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:48:48.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"31a24d58814c9641cd38ca1515cb053dee0cd174","tid":1481620,"uid":135408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:48:58.000Z","msg":"818要見到大家呀！"},{"pid":"f8b78f7a48950a14f67a03203ffd947dfe8ca123","tid":1481620,"uid":112748,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:50:05.000Z","msg":"正賤種"},{"pid":"32f1c075e2db793490f237befb920a34b30e8b36","tid":1481620,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:51:00.000Z","msg":"818見!"},{"pid":"c4d07c310f875bdbedd899cb405eafc41aefbffc","tid":1481620,"uid":268251,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:51:00.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNrEn9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNrEn9y.jpg&h=3a63f7b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原圖既少女, 係孤星淚入面既Cosette. 孤星淚係咩故事, 大家應該都知, 唔知自己google.<br />\n留意左好多文日, 我地既文宣其實可以利用唔同地方既文化,<br />\n加以更改, 達成更大效果. 要同全世界We Connect, 要活用唔同地方既文化.<br />\n孤星淚, 係歐美社會一定知道既title, 亦容易勾起佢地既共鳴.<br />\n大家不妨諗諗之後既文宣, 要更加creative.<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手forward去外國網站或者FB,<br />\n喺澳洲同法國既香港支持者受到大陸人攻擊之下,<br />\n呢張圖就係我地對外文宣既最佳利器.<br />\n當年南斯拉夫內戰, 打左幾年, 國際社會關注但唔出手,<br />\n最後係一張『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』既照片成為轉變關鍵.<br />\n羅密歐與茱麗葉既標題, 引起左歐美社會共鳴.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 發夢之歌: 自由之旗・自由之民, 一首代表我地理念既歌.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我地唔單止要宣傳, 仲要有理念. 藉由歌聲追求自由係最好既理念文宣,<br />\n唔會嚇親老一派既香港人, 亦可以觸動到歐美社會既支持.<br />\n我選呢首歌既理由, 同上面講既『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』一樣,<br />\n都係能觸動歐美普世價值既issue. 對我地黎講, 一首好歌,<br />\n可以鼓舞士氣, 提醒我地不要放棄.<br />\n<br />\n上面條LINK係我搵既一首歌, 好適合我地用. 大家可以襟上去聽下首歌,<br />\n如果認同既話, 我希望可以搞個萬人齊唱版, 大家可以聽住音樂清唱,<br />\n唱完之後UPLOAD上上面條連登LINK, 我整合之後放出黎.<br />\n<br />\n文宣也好, 歌曲也好, 最重要係做得到be Symbol.<br />\nBatman曾有一段對話:<br />\n&ldquo;People need dramatic examples to shake them out of apathy,<br />\nand I can&rsquo;t do that as Bruce Wayne. As a man I&rsquo;m flesh and blood,<br />\nI can be ignored, I can be destroyed, but as a symbol,<br />\nas a symbol I can be incorruptible. I can be everlasting.&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash; Bruce Wayne (Batman Begins)<br />\n<br />\n我地既文宣同理念, 一定要做到be Symbol, 一聽到某D文宣圖就諗起成個運動,<br />\n一聽到某首歌就能夠代表我地. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">be Symbol, be Symbol, be Symbol</span></span>.<br />\n重要事情講三次.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n818，維園見"},{"pid":"89a144e4931d8844aec2f98b60ddfe50c91b58bf","tid":1481620,"uid":23587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘔心到"},{"pid":"5e001b29a83c10e61517f6301de9fcc1caedda2a","tid":1481620,"uid":55130,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:51:13.000Z","msg":"勁<br />\n咁快整番好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f1389d0bacff09816827d4ea1993e040b242df","tid":1481620,"uid":135408,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d07c310f875bdbedd899cb405eafc41aefbffc","tid":1481620,"uid":268251,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:51:00.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNrEn9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNrEn9y.jpg&h=3a63f7b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原圖既少女, 係孤星淚入面既Cosette. 孤星淚係咩故事, 大家應該都知, 唔知自己google.<br />\n留意左好多文日, 我地既文宣其實可以利用唔同地方既文化,<br />\n加以更改, 達成更大效果. 要同全世界We Connect, 要活用唔同地方既文化.<br />\n孤星淚, 係歐美社會一定知道既title, 亦容易勾起佢地既共鳴.<br />\n大家不妨諗諗之後既文宣, 要更加creative.<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手forward去外國網站或者FB,<br />\n喺澳洲同法國既香港支持者受到大陸人攻擊之下,<br />\n呢張圖就係我地對外文宣既最佳利器.<br />\n當年南斯拉夫內戰, 打左幾年, 國際社會關注但唔出手,<br />\n最後係一張『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』既照片成為轉變關鍵.<br />\n羅密歐與茱麗葉既標題, 引起左歐美社會共鳴.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 發夢之歌: 自由之旗・自由之民, 一首代表我地理念既歌.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t